# --- m-standard sources policy (per spec §4.4) ----------------------------
# Default-conservative: bulk source content is excluded until Phase A0
# verifies redistribution rights for each source. Once verified, flip the
# relevant block: drop the ignore and commit the local replica.
#
# What is *always* tracked under sources/:
#   - manifest.tsv         (URL -> local path -> sha256 -> fetch_at)
#   - fetch.sh             (recreates the local replica from upstream)
#   - README.md / NOTICE   (license + acquisition notes)

# AnnoStd: crawled offline mirror
sources/anno/site/

# YottaDB documentation: full clone of the upstream docs repository
sources/ydb/repo/
